        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Shin Ho Yoon, a powerful god responsible for shaping human destinies, faces an unusual task of writing a romantic fate. Intrigued by a future screenplay penned by drama writer Go Chae Kyung, he decides to borrow ideas from it. In his divine plan, he pairs Chae Kyung with the nearly perfect Jung Ba Reum, a fortunate TV producer. Disguised as her landlord, Shin Ho Yoon aims to unite them but unexpectedly finds\n\nhimself falling for her, jeopardizing his own scheme.",
